div class="t m228f xe h4 y1ed3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the vast assembly, He seated Himself, on .the grass, and the </div><div class="t m485 xe h4 y110a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disciples and the- multitude followed His example. </div><div class="t m973 x71 h4 y14da ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The disciples&apos; place, was always next to Jesus. The people, </div><div class="t m4c xb6 h4 y1cbc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t mcf0 xe h4 y1504 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">constantly pressed upon Him, Vet the disciples&apos; understood that </div><div class="t mf47 xe h4 y1e40 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">they were not to </div><div class="t m5 xb h4 y1e40 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t mf54 x40 h4 y1e40 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">crowded away from &apos;His pregente.&quot;</div><div class="t md77 x4d h4 y1e40 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7</div><div class="t m200 x8d h4 y1e40 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-&quot;Thi. </div><div class="t m121 xe h30 y1ccb ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Desire of Ages,&quot; pp. 298, 299. </div><div class="t ma50 x71 h4 y1d36 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Beatitudes are usually undeistood to be eight in number. </div><div class="t m6ef xe h4 y1ce8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 5 : 3-10. The word &quot;Beatitude&quot; comes from the Latin </div><div class="t m3ac xe h30 y1194 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beatus, </div><div class="t mf21 x4e h4 y1dc7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">meaning a state of supreme blessedness. </div><div class="t m997 xf h4 yc84 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Suggestions </div><div class="t m9c3 x6a h13 y1546 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for Daily </div><div class="t m9a1 x79 h2f y1546 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Family.. </div><div class="t mde xb0 h13 y12ff ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Study </div><div class="t m7a0 x71 h13 yfd6 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m1629 x48 h13 yfd6 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read </div><div class="t m18ee x5b h2f y1f4c ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the &quot;Setting of the Lesson.&quot